name: AlligatorFinder
0:
”Alexa, launch alligator finder”
”Alexa, ask Alligator Finder to find the gators”
”Alexa, ask Alligator Finder where are the gators”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: alligator finder
des:
Disclaimer: this skill is a prank skill for entertainment purposes only and does not provide the ability to find alligators.

If you suffer from Gatorphobia, you want to know where the gators are, so you can be somewhere else. Ask Alexa where they are! For your entertainment, Alexa will respond with a random location nearby where she believes the gators are hiding. 

Note: If you have a real crocodile infestation, this skill will not help you avoid real live actual crocodiles.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
